<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:09:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列购买了一个大规模在线影响力系统来对抗反犹太主义和哈马斯暴行的否认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</link><description>10 月 7 日后不久，国防、情报和民间机构意识到，他们正在输给据消息人士称哈马斯“运转良好的心理和信息战机器”的在线战斗。因此，尽管担心未来政治滥用，他们还是悄悄购买了数字工具来打击虚假信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</guid></item><item><title>拉法过境点也可能是巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙的路线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</link><description>埃及担心以色列对过境点的控制将剥夺开罗在加沙的关键影响力。将其移交给巴勒斯坦权力机构可能会减轻这些担忧并有助于恢复加沙地带的正常状态 - 但目前不太可能发生</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</guid></item><item><title>拉阿纳纳袭击可能预示着来自动荡的约旦河西岸的一波巴勒斯坦恐怖浪潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</link><description>经济危机还可能导致针对巴勒斯坦权力机构的暴力爆发——以色列国防军担心局势可能会恶化——但很难想象内塔尼亚胡会允许西岸工人进入该国 ■ 以色列正在逐步减少在加沙的军事存在，但无法在新的人质释放协议上取得进展</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；伊朗声称袭击了伊拉克库尔德地区的“摩萨德总部”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，已通知两名人质的家人，他们的生命受到严重关切 ■ 以色列国防部长表示，停火只会危及人质，呼吁军事行动结束后在加沙采取外交解决方案 ■ 两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军枪击身亡 ■ 以色列国防军从加沙地带战斗中撤出作战师 ■ 胡塞武装袭击美国运营的船只后，也门荷台达机场附近传来爆炸声 ■ 以色列中部城市拉阿纳纳发生恐怖袭击，一名妇女死亡，十四人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在爱荷华州获胜演讲中表示，如果他是总统，哈马斯就不会攻击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</link><description>前总统击败对手赢得 2024 年首届共和党总统竞选</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</guid></item><item><title>政府争执推迟向加沙地带哈马斯扣押的以色列人质支付工资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</link><description>10 月 7 日后 100 多天，各部委之间关于如何支付俘虏工资的分歧仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨的 MKs 对他向内塔尼亚胡及其极右翼盟友投降感到沮丧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</link><description>几名政党议员表示，执政联盟中的其他政党曾多次利用其内阁多数席位来违反与民族团结的协议。一位人士表示，“我们总是在自己选择的战斗中失败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 21:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队通知两名哈马斯扣押人质的家人，严重关切他们的生命安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</link><description>“伊泰不是被我们部队射杀的，”以色列国防军发言人在哈马斯播放了伊泰和两名人质的视频一天后的新闻发布会上说。他补充说：“回想起来，我们知道我们袭击的目标就在他们被关押的地点附近。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 20:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列军队炮火打死；士兵记录下将男子踢倒在地的记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-by-idf-fire-in-west-bank-soldiers-seen-kicking-man-on-ground/0000018d-0e33-de9c-a3df-6ffbee730000</link><description>据报道，在与以色列军队的冲突中，一名 24 岁的妇女站在附近的一座建筑物上，被以色列国防军士兵开枪打死。在另一起事件中，一名巴勒斯坦男子被以色列国防军的炮火打死</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 19:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-by-idf-fire-in-west-bank-soldiers-seen-kicking-man-on-ground/0000018d-0e33-de9c-a3df-6ffbee730000</guid></item><item><title>他们是犹太反犹太复国主义者，但他们不是巴勒斯坦事业的盟友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-15/ty-article/.highlight/theyre-jewish-anti-zionists-but-theyre-no-ally-of-the-palestinian-cause/0000018d-0e48-d71c-ad9f-4fcaeb160000</link><description>巴勒斯坦运动不应该与 Neturei Karta 建立桥梁，后者的意识形态要求巴勒斯坦国是一个临时国家，无论他们多么愿意将自己标记化</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 19:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-15/ty-article/.highlight/theyre-jewish-anti-zionists-but-theyre-no-ally-of-the-palestinian-cause/0000018d-0e48-d71c-ad9f-4fcaeb160000</guid></item><item><title>“处于内爆的边缘”：以色列军队将精锐部队从加沙转移到约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-brink-of-implosion-israeli-army-transfers-elite-unit-out-of-gaza-to-west-bank/0000018d-0e2b-de9c-a3df-6ffbf7c90000</link><description>以色列国防军认为，该部队离开加沙是加沙战斗中失去重要力量的原因，但认为在约旦河西岸局势升级之际，这是必要的。消息人士称，这可归因于政府未能决定改善巴勒斯坦财政状况的措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:30:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-brink-of-implosion-israeli-army-transfers-elite-unit-out-of-gaza-to-west-bank/0000018d-0e2b-de9c-a3df-6ffbf7c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院撤销对在社交媒体上批评以色列国防军的高中教师的解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-reverses-dismissal-of-high-school-teacher-who-criticized-idf-on-social-media/0000018d-0dbd-d71c-ad9f-4fbfe0390000</link><description>法官裁定市政府没有提供解雇的正当理由，并补充说哈马斯袭击和加沙战争不会改变“教师言论自由的界限”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-reverses-dismissal-of-high-school-teacher-who-criticized-idf-on-social-media/0000018d-0dbd-d71c-ad9f-4fbfe0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府批准2024年战时国家预算；五位部长投反对票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-government-approves-updated-2024-state-budget-five-ministers-vote-against/0000018d-0e0e-d71c-ad9f-4f8ef8e10000</link><description>本尼·甘茨领导的民族团结党的部长们反对拟议的预算，因为缩小政府部门规模和冻结议员工资的要求没有得到满足</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-government-approves-updated-2024-state-budget-five-ministers-vote-against/0000018d-0e0e-d71c-ad9f-4f8ef8e10000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对内塔尼亚胡感到愤怒和沮丧。但他有改变路线的现实选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-angry-and-frustrated-with-netanyahu-he-has-realistic-options-to-change-course/0000018d-0d2e-de9c-a3df-6ffffc000000</link><description>迄今为止，美国总统一直拒绝放弃明确支持以色列加沙战争的呼吁，该战争现已进入第三个月。内塔尼亚胡无休止的自利和固执将使他在拜登行动时成为失败者</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-angry-and-frustrated-with-netanyahu-he-has-realistic-options-to-change-course/0000018d-0d2e-de9c-a3df-6ffffc000000</guid></item><item><title>完整地图：红海中也门胡塞武装袭击的所有船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/30-attacks-all-red-sea-ships-targeted-by-the-houthis/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</link><description>在伊朗的支持下，也门胡塞武装使用巡航导弹、无人机和反舰弹道导弹瞄准以色列人拥有的船只或他们确定正在前往以色列的船只</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:36:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/30-attacks-all-red-sea-ships-targeted-by-the-houthis/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》记者 Hagar Shezaf 荣获以色列新闻学院奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/haaretz-journalist-hagar-shezaf-awarded-israel-press-institute-prize/0000018d-0dd0-db13-affd-7df561600000</link><description>该奖项授予以色列记者“杰出、勇敢和不妥协的新闻报道”，并引用了谢扎夫对以色列极端定居者对约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的系统性袭击的报道</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/haaretz-journalist-hagar-shezaf-awarded-israel-press-institute-prize/0000018d-0dd0-db13-affd-7df561600000</guid></item><item><title>以北爱尔兰的教训能否解决以巴问题？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/can-the-israel-palestinians-troubles-be-solved-with-a-lesson-from-northern-ireland/0000018d-0ca5-daa5-a7cf-dee7451d0000</link><description>北爱尔兰的德里是成功但冷淡的和平的活生生的例子——没有人际和平的政治和平。我们爱上了和解努力，但犹太人和巴勒斯坦人的内心仍将存在冲突</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:26:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/can-the-israel-palestinians-troubles-be-solved-with-a-lesson-from-northern-ireland/0000018d-0ca5-daa5-a7cf-dee7451d0000</guid></item><item><title>“阿维胡在加沙”：进入加沙并被以色列国防军误杀的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/avihu-is-in-gaza-the-israeli-who-entered-gaza-and-was-mistakenly-killed-by-the-idf/0000018d-0d91-de9c-a3df-6ff9998f0000</link><description>数百名恐怖分子越过边境围栏屠杀平民两周后，29 岁的阿维胡·莫里 (Avihu Mori) 畅通无阻地步行半公里进入加沙，直到被以色列国防军杀害。两个月后，他的家人仍在等待这位前士兵如何越过边境围栏的答案</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/avihu-is-in-gaza-the-israeli-who-entered-gaza-and-was-mistakenly-killed-by-the-idf/0000018d-0d91-de9c-a3df-6ff9998f0000</guid></item><item><title>因 Instagram 故事而被拘留的阿拉伯裔以色列记者被软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-detained-for-instagram-story-released-to-house-arrest/0000018d-0cee-db13-affd-7def48b90000</link><description>塔里克·塔哈 (Tareq Taha) 是阿拉伯新闻“Arab 48”的编辑，也是海法理工大学的学生，因在以色列武装学生的照片上张贴巴勒斯坦国旗而被捕。他的律师说，“他反对伤害犹太人和巴勒斯坦人，并不是每个帖子都是煽动的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-detained-for-instagram-story-released-to-house-arrest/0000018d-0cee-db13-affd-7def48b90000</guid></item><item><title>随着爱荷华州预选会议的开始，共和党候选人尼基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 和罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 将以色列和加沙作为大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-iowa-caucuses-kick-off-gop-candidates-haley-desantis-use-israel-and-gaza-as-a-cudgel/0000018d-0cde-d71c-ad9f-4fded9040000</link><description>两位共和党总统候选人正在争夺仅次于领先者特朗普的第二名 — — 在共和党寻求巩固其亲以色列立场之际，他们将以色列和反犹太主义武器化，以包抄对方</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-iowa-caucuses-kick-off-gop-candidates-haley-desantis-use-israel-and-gaza-as-a-cudgel/0000018d-0cde-d71c-ad9f-4fded9040000</guid></item></channel></rss>